snippet     share
abbr        share
prev_word      '^'
    ${1:name}: &name
        ${2}
    <<: *${3:name}

snippet     socket
abbr database.ymlのsocketをすべての環境に対応する
  <%
  socket = ["/tmp/mysqld.sock",
            "/tmp/mysql.sock",
            "/var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock",
            "/var/lib/mysql/mysql.sock",
            "/opt/local/var/run/mysql5/mysqld.sock"
            ].detect{|socket| File.exist?(socket)}
  %>

